----------------------------------------------------------------------
README
----------------------------------------------------------------------

This example creates a homogeneous halfspace model, using the parallel decomposer.
It runs by default on 8 MPI processes.

step-by-step tutorial:

1. go to this example directory:

     > cd EXAMPLES/decompose_mesh_MPI/


2. run simulation:
    
   - run script:
     > ./run_this_example.sh


Compare your seismograms in OUTPUT_FILES/ with the reference ones in directory REF_SEIS/

